data.description: Welcome to Heritage Grove in Covington. Well maintained home in a wonderful location featuring 4 bedrooms plus office/den. Covered front porch area for relaxing in the evening, large open kitchen with plenty of room for the pickiest chef, family room with cozy fireplace. Formal dining area, formal living area, and all bedrooms located on upper floor away from the noise of daily life! Primary with private bath and large closet. Low maintenance backyard, so not a lot of yard work in the summer!! So sit back and enjoy!
